Defeat wargs and warg-masters in Râkh Mathán

The hillside at Râkh Mathán is home to many Wargs. Their dens extend up into the hills where the beasts are bred and trained by cruel Orcs. These Wargs, and the Orcs who train them, must be cleared out if the woods of Rath Dúath are to ever be safe for Faramir's scouts.
You did much to hinder the Wargs in Râkh Mathán. Those who fight for Gondor in the Morgul Vale surely thank you for your efforts.
Defeat many wargs and warg-masters in Râkh Mathán.
The dwellings of Wargs extends up into the hills where they are bred and trained by cruel Orcs.
Warg dens litter the hills of the Rath Dúath, but the wargs are not alone. Orcs have bred and trained the beasts to follow their master's lash.
